[32m+[m[32m### ⚖️ Decisions Made[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### Use Reverse Proxy instead of Direct Ports[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Pros:**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Clean URLs (no ports)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Centralized routing[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Matches real-world production setups[m[41m [m
[32m+[m[32m- **Cons:**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Adds complexity (can break with misconfig)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Decision:** Use reverse proxy → necessary for scaling + professionalism[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### Keep Services Internal (VPN-only)[m
