[32m+[m[32m  - Avoids exposing home network publicly[m[41m [m
[32m+[m[32m- **Cons:**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Requires VPN for access[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Decision:** VPN-first architecture → security over convenience[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### Run Services in Docker[m
