[32m+[m[32m  - Consistency across services[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Easier deployment + rebuild[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Cons:**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Permissions + networking issues can break things[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Decision:** Continue using Docker → industry standard skill[m
